      axiosCode: `<span class="text-blue-400">axios</span>.<span class="text-blue-400">get</span>(<span class="text-emerald-400">'https://axomock.dev/api/posts?sortBy=title&order=asc'</span>)\n  .<span class="text-blue-400">then</span>(res => <span class="text-blue-400">console</span>.log(res.data));`,
